Title: How do I programmatically reposition monitors in a multiple-monitor system?
Description: Say you’re looking to write a tool to manipulate monitor positions. What functions should you be calling? The function to call is Change­Display­Settings­Ex with a DEVMODE whose dmFields has the DM_POSITION flag set. Put the desired upper left corner of the monitor in the dmPosition.x and dmPosition.y fields.
